features: 【Easy Snack Accessibility】Say goodbye to the struggle of reaching for your snacks with this Snack Tray for Stanley 30 OZ Cup with handle. The snack tray’s five food compartments allow you to conveniently hold various snacks like popcorn, fries, chips, nuts and melon seeds, ensuring you can enjoy your favorite treats without compromising your drink.

【Effortless Installation】The Snack Bowl for Stanley 30 oz tumbler is incredibly easy to install. Simply press it into the cup handle, making it a perfect fit for your car cup holder. Whether you're driving with your family or on a solo trip, you can now enjoy snacks along with your juice or soda, adding a delightful twist to your journey.

【Versatile Snacking】Whether you're at home, at the cinema, at a stadium, on a business trip, traveling, or in your car, this snack holder for Stanley 30 OZ Cup is your ideal companion. The snack ring allows you to indulge in snacks and beverages without the need for separate containers, making it convenient to satisfy your cravings anytime, anywhere.

【Tailored for Stanley Cups】Designed exclusively for Stanley 30 oz tumbler with handle, this snack tray fits both 1.0 and 2.0 cups seamlessly, ensuring optimal performance. If you plan to use it with other tumbler cups, remember to measure the cup's diameter before making your purchase.

【Premium Silicone Construction】The Snack Tray for 30 oz Stanley Cup crafted from high quality food-grade silicone, this snack bowl is BPA-free, soft and safe for children. They are not only reusable and durable but also fit snugly in the cup's mouth, preventing wobbling or accidental falls. Additionally, silicone's heat resistance and dishwasher-safe nature make maintenance a breeze.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 31, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars My daughter found it hilarous.
reviews.reviewText: Like every girl, my daughter had to have a Stanley cup. I don't understand it because I'm old and not hip. I grabbed this snack tray for her, because I thought it was funny, and the girl is known for eating tons of grapes and other fruit, so I thought that this made a good grape holder. She found the gift to be hilarious, and acknowledged that it will be a great place to store grapes and Craisins while watching TV. It seems to be made well, and should hold up, but I'll be back to update this if that proves to be untrue.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 8, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Hilarioius Addition to Bunco Night
reviews.reviewText: My friends and I all have these Stanley style 40 ounce tumblers. So, as a joke, I got one of these snack trays for each one of us at Bunco. It was hilarious when I gifted them to each one of the gals. They were mocking them at first, but quickly realized how handy they really are, as there's never a good spot at the bunco table for your drink AND a snack plate. Love it!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 7, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Easy to put on. Regulates your snacking
reviews.reviewText: This is easy to put on. It’s soft and pliable. Although I would like it to be much bigger it is better that it is not. This is good for regulating my snacking. I can do some serious snacking, which never ends well. This keeps me from eating the whole bag or box of goodies. This will be nice in the car for Fast food. Fries and ketchup contained in the compartments. This is a fun and helpful little gadget.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 17, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars So cool, very handy.
reviews.reviewText: Such a brilliant idea! Holds a good amount of snacks. Silicone bowl with 5 separated sections. Actually fits very securely, it stabilizes nicely over the cup handle. Also comes with a little cloud straw topper as well. Such a cute set that is extremely useful as well! Obviously you would use this snack bowl with drinks you intend to drink through the straw, as you couldn't tip the cup to drink from, with snacks in the bowl. But very brilliant and convenient.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 2, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Fits perfectly, so sturdy, holds a ton
reviews.reviewText: This is the best accessory I've gotten for my 40 oz tumbler so far. It fits snugly and perfectly. The way it rests on the handle gives it good support. The black is a nice color and it didn't get any kind of film on it after washing it in the dishwasher. It held its shape perfectly too. This thing holds a TON of snacks, so my whole family can snack on different things from the 4 different compartments. I love this thing.

Ever felt like your snack game was missing that special something? Enter the Snack Tray for Stanley 30 oz Cup. This quirky little accessory is a munchie mastermind, turning your drink into a snack-serving hero. With compartments for popcorn, nuts, and whatever else tickles your fancy, it's like having a mini buffet at your fingertips. The silicone build is soft yet surprisingly sturdy, clinging to your cup like a koala to a tree. And it's a breeze to clean, which is a win in my book. But, there's a little hiccup - it seems like the cloud straw topper sometimes goes on a little adventure of its own, leaving you wondering where it wandered off to.This snack tray is a nifty little companion for your Stanley cup, perfect for those who like their snacks organized and accessible. It's functional, fun, and a bit of a conversation starter. Just be aware that you might need to play detective with the straw topper. Overall, a solid pick for snack enthusiasts.

The bowl arrived, fit perfectly on the mug. The only problem is that it's advertised as coming with a cloud straw topper. Unfortunately that never came. Don't know if anyone else has had this issue or not, but the order is incomplete.
